<br>
As they got closer to a more populated area, Rayne stopped her. <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;Ok Taylee, here is the deal...</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> She listened as the dhampire laid out their possible plan of action, and when she finished, added slyly, <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;Unless you have other ideas? Another blood source?&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
Taylee looked at the girl standing with her hands on her hips and smirked at the last comment. &quot;No, I don't have another source...I'll keep you to that promise you so gracously gave me, earlier,&quot; the blonde answered her with a soft laugh. She knew it must be driving the redhead crazy. &quot;But your plan sounds like it'll work....just make sure you're still here when I do lead a vamp this way.&quot;<br>
<br>
Taylee turned and began to walk towards the small store. She still didn't totally trust Rayne, but she figured the girl wasn't letting her walk into a trap. Not when this could benefit her as well. <br>
<br>
'Damn,' Taylee thought as she pushed her was through the double doors, 'When was the last time I ate?' She knew it had been down in the underground city, with....Vania...&quot;Fuck,&quot; she swore softly, thinking, 'What happened to her?' but she didn't have time right now to worry about the lost girl.<br>
<br>
Grabbing a couple of items from the sparse contents of the shelves, Taylee made her way to the front of the store. Then putting her things down on the counter, she fished in the pocket of her coat, bringing out a couple of wadded up bills, hoping it would enough. The old lady behind the counter scooped them up greedily off the counter with a grunt and after bagging the blonde girl's purchases, handed her a small amount of change. Taylee sighed, stuffing it back in her pocket. 'So much for having any money left,' she thought making her way out into the dark.<br>
<br>
Slowly walking away from the lights, Taylee could almost feel the eyes that followed her. God, she hoped Rayne was close, because the prickling of her skin told her someone was behind her. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bkalaberia.showUserPublicProfile?gid=taylea>Taylea</A> at: 10/12/03 4:07 pm<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm47.showMessageRange?topicID=2.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm47.showNextMessage?topicID=2.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm47.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=34><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/space/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm47.emailToFriend?topicID=2.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm47.threadControl?topicID=2.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/space/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm47.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm47.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email